_sText:
This is the final version of de_pasdequartier. 

Added soundscapes so you no longer play in silence, and added better placed cubemaps for better reflections. 

Add more background detail.

Lowered the framerate across the map and fixed bugs such as roof climbing.

Added more defend points to B so its harder to rush. 

Moved some spawn points and objects around to balance out the map.

Original map http://gamebanana.com/css/maps/14248
